high_descs: Go to the side of the island across from the mirror.
Pick up the knife on the island.
Take the knife to the sink.
Slice the potato in the center of the sink.
Go to the counter in front of the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Go to the microwave.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave.
Take the cooked potato slice to the sink.
Put the hot potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go around the island counter and turn right to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go around the island counter to the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Turn around and go back around the island counter to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around and go back around the room to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around and head back to the microwave.
Cook the potato in the microwave and then pick it back up.
Turn left and go back around the room to the sink.
Put the slice of potato in the sink in front of the whole potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the right, around the island, to where the knife is
Pick up the knife from the island
Turn right, walk back to the sink on the left
Slice the potato in the sink
Turn around and walk the knife back around the island to the microwave
Open the microwave, place the knife inside
Turn to the right, walk around the island back to the sink
Pick up a potato slice from the sink
Turn to the right, walk back around the island to the microwave
Open the microwave, place the potato in, heat, then remove the potato slice again
Turn to the right, walk around the island back to the sink
Place the warmed slice of potato into the sink
anns.task_desc: Warm a slice of potato  in the microwave
